# WebZNC Web IRC client for ZNC bouncer

This client runs as standaloe app and allows connection from mobile/desktop to ZNC with buffer replay and HTTP BASIC and URL parameter auth and channel to be loaded

?auth=KEY

?auth=KEY&channel=CHANNEL

All config is in the PY file and can also be done by ENV vars as described there, SSL with self signed cert is supported.

This server supports running stsandaloe at / on the specified port as well as under /znc behind a reverse proxy (if you want to use another directory seartch for /znc and change it).
